        <h5>Hotel/Travel Package — November 10–14</h5>
    <p>Packages start at <strong>$999</strong> from Portland.<br />
      <strong>Contact Tom Conkrite today,</strong> 1-866-611-3785 or <a href="mailto:tom@tomtravel.net">email tom@tomtravel.net</a>, for travel information and travel registration. </p>
    <h5>CLE Program — November 12</h5>
    <p><strong>• $395</strong> per person (CLE registration required with travel package; $450 after October 11)<br />
